bbox": [856.3, 1002.5, 1513.8, 1022.7]}, {"text": "operations and relocation of this portion of Zebra’s business from the U.S. to China and", "bbox": [856.3, 1023.3, 1560.3, 1043.5]}, {"text": "consolidating some activities domestically.", "bbox": [856.3, 1044.1, 1206.3, 1064.3]}, {"text": "Costs incurred through December 31, 2013 and costs expected to be incurred relate to the", "bbox": [856.3, 1083.7, 1576.9, 1103.9]}, {"text": "following: restructuring of Zebra’s manufacturing operations; relocation of a significant", "bbox": [856.3, 1104.6, 1559.9, 1124.7]}, {"text": "portion of Zebra’s supply chain operations from the U.S. to China; consolidating activities", "bbox": [856.3, 1125.4, 1576.8, 1145.6]}, {"text": "domestically; restructuring of our sales operations; restructuring certain corporate", "bbox": [856.3, 1146.2, 1522.8, 1166.4]}, {"text": "functions; and amending the location solutions “2012 restructuring plan” by adding", "bbox": [856.3, 1167.1, 1529.6, 1187.2]}, {"text": "additional restructuring charges to be incurred.", "bbox": [856.3, 1187.9, 1239.9, 1208.1]}]}